---
title: Smoky Lentil Tacos with Charred Corn and Peppers
description: It's taco night and these veggie lentil bundles do not disappoint! Soft tortillas are stuffed to the brim with chipotle lentils, sweet corn, juicy poblanos and salty feta. Saddle up and dig in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tacos-aux-lentilles-fumees-4ea78ff2.jpg
